      public byte[] achVendId()

    • setAchVendId

      public void setAchVendId(byte[] b)
      Sets the achVendId field. This field is 4 bytes in length and only the first 4 bytes of the byte array will be written. If the byte array is less than 4 bytes it will be padded out with space characters (0x20).
      参数:
      b - ach Vendor Id
